<div class="format_text" id="comment-body-2101">
<p>And knowledgeable people who recognize that they are, according to the IRC, and USC Title 26, and all related Supreme Court Decisions, NON-taxpayers, pay even less than either an employee, employer, or independent contractor.</p>
<p>This country of supposedly independent States, united, under a Constitution, needs more Tax attorneys and CPA&#8217;s who actually have read, and understand, the IRC and Title 26.</p>
</div>
